content_text: My role model is APJ Abdul Kalam Becauses. He contributes his knowledge, his everything towards the growth of the country and he gives good lessons as well. For us one of them like few of them are like we have to be focused, we have to be dedicated person to grow in our life and always with we need to try to contribute our knowledge. We always try to contribute towards the growth of our country and society because it is very important. Alone you cannot do. Everything.
